    <stitle>International&#174; MaxxForce&#8482; DT, 9 and 10 Engine Service Manual - Oil System Module Assembly -
        Exploded View and Description
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>Exploded View and Description</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="1">
            <title>Service Procedure</title>
            <figure id="f3350010248" figsize="pg-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figK13/K13003.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="472px" box="no"/>
                <caption>Oil system module assembly</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Turbocharger oil supply tube fitting and O-ring</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">O-ring</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Regulator valve assembly (oil pressure)</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Thermal valve assembly (oil)</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">M8 x 20 bolt (2)</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Oil cooler housing</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Coolant seal</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Irregular gasket (oil)</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">M18 plug assembly (coolant drain)</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Coolant seal (2)</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Oil seal</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">O-ring</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Lube filter adapter</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">M8 x 25 bolt (3)</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">M8 x 20 bolt (8)</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Cooler heat exchanger (23 or 33 plates)</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Filter bypass valve</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">O-ring</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">M12 plug assembly (oil priming)</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <para>The oil system module assembly uses engine coolant, a heat exchanger, and a thermal oil valve to cool
                engine oil. An oil pressure regulator valve dumps excess oil to the oil pan to regulate oil pressure and
                an oil filter filters engine oil. See
                <hotlnk document="eges3351_15.xml" xrefid="s0119">Engine Lubrication System</hotlnk>
                <xref refid="s0119"/>
                for additional lubrication system details.
            </para>
        </svcproc>
